---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="How Selcurate handles your data and privacy.">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-h1 font-bold font-heading text-foreground mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-foreground-muted mb-8">Last updated: April 2026</p>

    <div class="prose">
      <h2>Data We Collect</h2>

      <p>
        <strong>Email addresses:</strong> If you subscribe to our newsletter, we collect
        your email address. This is stored by our email service provider (Buttondown) and
        used solely to send you our weekly newsletter. You can unsubscribe at any time.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Analytics:</strong> We use Google Analytics 4 to understand how visitors
        use our site. This collects anonymized data including pages visited, time on site,
        and referral source. No personally identifiable information is collected through
        analytics. Analytics cookies are only set after you accept them via the consent banner.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Cookies:</strong> We use cookies for analytics (GA4) and to remember your
        cookie consent preference. See our <a href="/cookie-policy/">Cookie Policy</a> for details.
      </p>

      <h2>How We Use Your Data</h2>
      <p>
        Email addresses are used exclusively for sending our newsletter. We do not sell,
        share, or rent your data to third parties.
      </p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>
        You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data at
        any time by contacting <a href="mailto:hello@selcurate.com">hello@selcurate.com</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Malaysia PDPA 2010 Compliance</h2>
      <p>
        This site is operated from Malaysia and complies with the Personal Data Protection
        Act 2010 (PDPA). For PDPA-related inquiries, contact the Department of Personal
        Data Protection (JPDP) at <a href="https://www.pdp.gov.my/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">pdp.gov.my</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>GDPR (EU Visitors)</h2>
      <p>
        If you are in the EU/EEA, you have rights under GDPR including access,
        rectification, erasure, and data portability. Contact
        <a href="mailto:hello@selcurate.com">hello@selcurate.com</a> to exercise these rights.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on
        this page with an updated date.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
